      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/Teknium/status/2067222815913447678",
      "tweet_text": "Making a change to the Hermes Agent Curator that will make it so it only Prunes unused skills by default, it will no longer consolidate skills unless you opt in in the config or dashboard.\\n\\nIt was costing upwards of 16$ per week to operate for some using frontier models and causing some confusion for other users. This is a better middle ground for a default scenario.",
